title: Connector for photoelectric conversion

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a connector for photoelectric conversion, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a top, front and left side perspective view of a connector for photoelectric conversion, showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a bottom, rear and left side perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a rear elevation view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a left side elevation view thereof;
FIG. 8 is a right side elevation view thereof; and,
FIG. 9 is a top, front and left side perspective view thereof, in use condition.
The broken line showing of the environment is for illustrative purposes only and forms no part of the claimed design.
